+ 31. After an epic struggle by her gallant Master and escorts, S.S. OHIO entered Grand Harbour at 0755.

32. Force X’s withdrawal was uneventful in the initial stages. When off Cape Bon at 0130 they were attacked by E-Boats. These were engaged and an explosion was seen which was believed to. be an E-Boat blowing up.

33. At 0450 when off Fratelli Rock a U-Boat attacked the force, H.M.S. ASHANTI being just missed. H.M.S. KENYA sighted the sub- marine and made an attempt to ram but the submarine was inside her turning circle.
